data.description: Great opportunity to live close to Austin without Austin taxes! Low, 2.2% tax rate with City of Austin Utilities!  That means no M.U. D. Tax!  Top rated Pflugerville ISD Schools, close to parks, trails, and community pool.  This four bedroom floor plan works well with the primary suite separate from two of the secondary bedrooms and with the large 4th bedroom serving as an office/game room/studio/gym/etc., in the front of the home. No carpet!  Stained concrete and tile throughout is a necessity for allergy sufferers & pet owners. Open floor plan invites you in to the formal dining area as you enter the home.  Bright with natural light and spacious enough for large gatherings, your dining area may become the focal point of your home.  Leading into the well appointed kitchen, stainless appliances and a large walk in pantry are sure to offer an abundance of space to create meals for friends and family.  Finally commencing in the living area with tray ceilings and large windows, this 1429 sq. ft. lives like a much larger space!  Directly adjacent to the living area is the primary suite. Ensuite bath offers large soaking tub for relaxation. Two of the secondary bedrooms are located down the middle of the home hallway that leads to an oversized laundry room as well as a full bathroom. Minutes to IH 35, I30 Tollway, shopping, restaurants, and recreation. Newer roof and newer dishwasher add to the exceptional value of the home!
